oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Compilation of Carlos Salzedo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features harpist and composer Carlos Salzedo performing eight songs. The tape is from an unidentified date. This tape is thirty-seven of an unidentified number of tapes.
